cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on the efficient design of a segmentation decoder for automated driving, which falls under the computer vision and robotics domains. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of multi-task learning, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper proposes a novel layer design, which could fall under the neural and evolutionary computing sub-category, cs.NE.
